<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA1">
<l>piṟantumoḻi payiṉṟa piṉṉellāṅ kātaṟ</l>
<l>ciṟantuniṉ cēvaṭiyē cērntē - ṉiṟantikaḻu</l>
<l>maiññāṉṟa kaṇṭattu vāṉōr perumāṉē</l>
<l>yeññāṉṟu tīrppa tiṭar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
After being born [and] repeating words, exulting in the love
for all [things] I have joined your red feet, oh great lord of the celestials,
with a throat hung with black that shine with colour.
When will there be an end to affliction?
      </lg>
    </div>
